Parliament, Monday, 28 October 2019 – The Standing Committee on Public Accounts (Scopa), will tomorrow be briefed by the National Treasury on a consolidated report on deviations and expansions for national departments and entities for Quarter Four of 2018/19 and for the First Quarter of 2019/20.
	
	Details are as follows:
	Date: Tuesday, 29 October 2019
	Time: 09h30
	Venue: Committee Room V454, Fourth Floor, Old Assembly Building.
	
	ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES 
	
	For media enquiries, please contact the committee’s Media Officer:
